		<title>Ruby’s Top 10 of 2008: Thanking Those Who’ve Made Ruby Great This Year</title>
		<link>http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/RubyInside/~3/481309270/rubys-top-10-of-2008-thanking-those-whove-made-ruby-great-this-year-1393.html</link>
