		<title>Ruby Implementation Shootout: A Bright Future for Ruby Performance!</title>
		<link>http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/RubyInside/~3/479919374/ruby-implementation-shootout-a-bright-future-for-ruby-performance-1390.html</link>
		<comments>http://www.rubyinside.com/ruby-implementation-shootout-a-bright-future-for-ruby-performance-1390.html#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 09 Dec 2008 21:20:44 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Peter Cooper</dc:creator>
		
